    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Hey Listen</strong></i><strong>:</strong> The demo for this game is the full game. Only purchase if you want to support future games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WARNING:</strong> This game will destroy friendships.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i><strong>We Are Square</strong></i> you and up to seven friends must work together to control one square and platform yourselves to the goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316390/extras/b9130044e65ecafb241630f1c44d63ad.avif?t=1755361067\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316390/extras_big/b9130044e65ecafb241630f1c44d63ad.avif?t=1755361067 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exactly 1 music track!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 24 levels! (there are 25 levels... and some of them are jokes)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enough tricky platforming to make you hate your friends!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A &quot;Blame Screen&quot; after every death to let you know which of your friends is holding you back!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed for local co-op but works with Steam's Remote Play feature</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamepads are required. Due to coding weirdness, only 4 controllers can be Xbox controllers. For 5+ player gameplay, PlayStation or generic gamepads must be used.</p>",
